  "title": "Pointwise Absolute Value of a Function",
  "root": "",
  "statement": "Let $X\\subseteq\\mathbb{R}$ and let $f:X\\to\\mathbb{R}$. The pointwise\nabsolute value $|f|:X\\to\\mathbb{R}$ is the function defined by\n\\[\n |f|(x)=|f(x)|\n \\qquad (x\\in X).\n\\]",
